          </p>
            <h4><a href="http://gizmodo.com/9-vintage-vending-machines-from-a-time-when-theyd-sell-734051398?utm_campaign=socialflow_gizmodo_twitter&utm_source=gizmodo_twitter&utm_medium=socialflow " class="titlelink">Can I Interest You in a Snack? Perhaps a Beverage? </a></h4>
